---
// Process Component - No props needed
---

<section class="py-20 lg:py-28 bg-slate-50">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 xl:px-12">
    {/* Header */}
    <div class="text-center mb-16 lg:mb-20 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-white rounded-full border border-slate-200 mb-6">
        <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-slate-900 rounded-full"></span>
        <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 tracking-wide uppercase">How We Work</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 leading-tight">
        How We Work Together
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg lg:text-xl text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
        A clear process from discovery to delivery. No surprises, no hidden steps.
      </p>
    </div>

    {/* Timeline */}
    <div class="relative">
      {/* Timeline Line - Desktop */}
      <div class="hidden lg:block absolute left-1/2 top-0 bottom-0 w-0.5 bg-slate-300 -translate-x-1/2"></div>
      
      {/* Timeline Items */}
      <div class="space-y-8 lg:space-y-12">
        {/* Discovery */}
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="lg:grid lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-8 items-center">
            <div class="lg:text-right lg:pr-12 mb-4 lg:mb-0">
              <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 lg:p-8 border border-slate-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3 lg:justify-end">
                  <span class="lg:hidden w-8 h-8 bg-slate-900 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">1</span>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">Discovery</h3>
                </div>
                <p class="text-slate-600 mb-3">A business owner finds us through search, word of mouth, or referral.</p>
                <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1 bg-slate-100 text-slate-700 text-sm font-medium rounded-full">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                  </svg>
                  1-2 weeks
                </span>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            {/* Center Dot - Desktop */}
            <div class="hidden lg:flex absolute left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-4 h-4 bg-slate-900 rounded-full border-4 border-white shadow-md items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-xs font-bold text-white">1</span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="lg:pl-12 hidden lg:block"></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Self-Diagnosis */}
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="lg:grid lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-8 items-center">
            <div class="hidden lg:block lg:pr-12"></div>
            
            {/* Center Dot - Desktop */}
            <div class="hidden lg:flex absolute left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-4 h-4 bg-slate-900 rounded-full border-4 border-white shadow-md items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-xs font-bold text-white">2</span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="lg:pl-12 mb-4 lg:mb-0">
              <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 lg:p-8 border border-slate-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
                  <span class="lg:hidden w-8 h-8 bg-slate-900 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">2</span>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">Self-Diagnosis</h3>
                </div>
                <p class="text-slate-600 mb-3">They see their own problems clearly through our assessment. Most businesses fail 3+ technical checks.</p>
                <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1 bg-slate-100 text-slate-700 text-sm font-medium rounded-full">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                  </svg>
                  30 minutes
                </span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Contrast */}
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="lg:grid lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-8 items-center">
            <div class="lg:text-right lg:pr-12 mb-4 lg:mb-0">
              <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 lg:p-8 border border-slate-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3 lg:justify-end">
                  <span class="lg:hidden w-8 h-8 bg-slate-900 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">3</span>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">Contrast</h3>
                </div>
                <p class="text-slate-600 mb-3">They see a site built by this business with all technical checks green. They feel the gap themselves.</p>
                <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1 bg-slate-100 text-slate-700 text-sm font-medium rounded-full">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                  </svg>
                  1-2 hours
                </span>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            {/* Center Dot - Desktop */}
            <div class="hidden lg:flex absolute left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-4 h-4 bg-slate-900 rounded-full border-4 border-white shadow-md items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-xs font-bold text-white">3</span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="lg:pl-12 hidden lg:block"></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Enquiry */}
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="lg:grid lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-8 items-center">
            <div class="hidden lg:block lg:pr-12"></div>
            
            {/* Center Dot - Desktop */}
            <div class="hidden lg:flex absolute left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-4 h-4 bg-slate-900 rounded-full border-4 border-white shadow-md items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-xs font-bold text-white">4</span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="lg:pl-12 mb-4 lg:mb-0">
              <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 lg:p-8 border border-slate-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
                  <span class="lg:hidden w-8 h-8 bg-slate-900 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">4</span>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">Enquiry</h3>
                </div>
                <p class="text-slate-600 mb-3">They reach out. The conversation begins with shared understanding, not education.</p>
                <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1 bg-slate-100 text-slate-700 text-sm font-medium rounded-full">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                  </svg>
                  24-48 hours
                </span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Proposal */}
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="lg:grid lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-8 items-center">
            <div class="lg:text-right lg:pr-12 mb-4 lg:mb-0">
              <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 lg:p-8 border border-slate-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3 lg:justify-end">
                  <span class="lg:hidden w-8 h-8 bg-slate-900 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">5</span>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">Proposal</h3>
                </div>
                <p class="text-slate-600 mb-3">Simple, clear, defined scope and outcome. No ambiguity. Repeatable structure.</p>
                <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1 bg-slate-100 text-slate-700 text-sm font-medium rounded-full">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                  </svg>
                  2-3 days
                </span>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            {/* Center Dot - Desktop */}
            <div class="hidden lg:flex absolute left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-4 h-4 bg-slate-900 rounded-full border-4 border-white shadow-md items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-xs font-bold text-white">5</span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="lg:pl-12 hidden lg:block"></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Build */}
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="lg:grid lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-8 items-center">
            <div class="hidden lg:block lg:pr-12"></div>
            
            {/* Center Dot - Desktop */}
            <div class="hidden lg:flex absolute left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-4 h-4 bg-slate-900 rounded-full border-4 border-white shadow-md items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-xs font-bold text-white">6</span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="lg:pl-12 mb-4 lg:mb-0">
              <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 lg:p-8 border border-slate-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
                  <span class="lg:hidden w-8 h-8 bg-slate-900 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">6</span>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">Build</h3>
                </div>
                <p class="text-slate-600 mb-3">Full stack implementation. Astro, Sanity, Schema, Lead Layer. No shortcuts regardless of project size.</p>
                <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1 bg-slate-100 text-slate-700 text-sm font-medium rounded-full">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                  </svg>
                  2-4 weeks
                </span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Delivery */}
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="lg:grid lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-8 items-center">
            <div class="lg:text-right lg:pr-12 mb-4 lg:mb-0">
              <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 lg:p-8 border border-slate-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3 lg:justify-end">
                  <span class="lg:hidden w-8 h-8 bg-slate-900 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">7</span>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">Delivery</h3>
                </div>
                <p class="text-slate-600 mb-3">Technical verification on handover day. Every check green. Before and after documented.</p>
                <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1 bg-slate-100 text-slate-700 text-sm font-medium rounded-full">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                  </svg>
                  1 day
                </span>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            {/* Center Dot - Desktop */}
            <div class="hidden lg:flex absolute left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-4 h-4 bg-slate-900 rounded-full border-4 border-white shadow-md items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-xs font-bold text-white">7</span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="lg:pl-12 hidden lg:block"></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Referral Ask */}
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="lg:grid lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-8 items-center">
            <div class="hidden lg:block lg:pr-12"></div>
            
            {/* Center Dot - Desktop */}
            <div class="hidden lg:flex absolute left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-4 h-4 bg-green-600 rounded-full border-4 border-white shadow-md items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-xs font-bold text-white">8</span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="lg:pl-12 mb-4 lg:mb-0">
              <div class="bg-green-50 rounded-2xl p-6 lg:p-8 border border-green-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
                  <span class="lg:hidden w-8 h-8 bg-green-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">8</span>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-green-900">Referral Ask</h3>
                </div>
                <p class="text-green-800 mb-3">One specific, direct ask at the moment of successful delivery.</p>
                <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1 bg-green-100 text-green-800 text-sm font-medium rounded-full">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                  </svg>
                  Immediate
                </span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    {/* Bottom CTA */}
    <div class="mt-16 lg:mt-20 text-center">
      <div class="bg-slate-900 text-white rounded-2xl p-8 lg:p-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-white/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold mb-4">The Relationship Continues</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-300 mb-8 leading-relaxed max-w-xl mx-auto">
          Quarterly check-ins, results updates, and ongoing support. The relationship stays warm because the value is ongoing, not because a contract forces it.
        </p>
        <a 
          href="/contact" 
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 bg-white text-slate-900 font-semibold rounded-xl hover:bg-slate-100 hover:shadow-lg hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 group"
        >
          <span>Start Your Journey</span>
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
